description.en:
What is the project about?

Shiba CEO,is a Meme token in the BSC ecosystem, $SHIBCEO is comunity-driven cannot controll by anyone. Shiba CEO - A decentralized cryptocurrency, with instant rewards for holders. 5% of each transaction will be shared among the holders

What makes your project unique?

$SHIBCEO a Meme token, Shiba CEO community is the strongest you can find, supporting each other and pushing each other towards success.

History of your project.


What’s next for your project?
We’ve been running marketing’s and partnerships and we are having Ama and spaces on telegram and twitter 


What can your token be used for?
